{"tid":956504,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"m43末日 Olympus出售中國子企 傳深圳易聯接棒","createTime":"2018-12-26T10:01:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-26T16:57:14.000Z","uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e9098f628c8460df4e5301aa2d193e29feecec65","tid":956504,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T10:01:34.000Z","msg":"日媒報道，<span style=\"color: red;\">奧林巴斯(Olympus)將於2019年6月出售負責數碼相機生産的中國子企奧林巴斯(深圳)工業，出售金額約300億日圓</span>，以應對智能手機普及，令數碼相機需求減少的現狀。 <br />\n<br />\n另內媒報道，奧林巴斯(深圳)工業全部股權將出售予Shenzhen YL Technology，股權轉讓所得收入將錄入截至2020年3月的財年。 <br />\n<br />\nShenzhen YL Technology據悉為深圳易聯技術有限公司，其背後實控人為新國都(300130.SZ)創辦人劉祥。 <br />\n<br />\n新國都股價回落0.1%，報11.88元人民幣。 <br />\n<br />\nm43啲撚樣死曬去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2850f35bf481ef71cf6c4bc0e81ca8aea3610dbf","tid":956504,"uid":191352,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T10:03:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8abe6243af5c81814a1bec01bf5f3196ff18560d","tid":956504,"uid":4673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T10:13:01.000Z","msg":"有乜問題？ OLYMPUS 一早撤出中國啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4/185852/olympus%E7%9B%B8%E6%A9%9F%E5%B7%A5%E5%BB%A0%E6%92%A4%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%A8%E8%B6%8A%E5%8D%97%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E9%2587%2591%25E8%259E%258D%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25A0%25B4%2F185852%2Folympus%25E7%259B%25B8%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%25BB%25A0%25E6%2592%25A4%25E5%2587%25BA%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E9%259B%2586%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%25A8%25E8%25B6%258A%25E5%258D%2597%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2594